      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">PxrAovLight is a handy utility light that allows a lighting artist to output a shot-specific AOV mask without needing to request one from the shading artists. In this example, we'll break down a common request...getting a refraction AOV for a character's eye (sclera or iris inside a cornea).</span></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">To simplify it further, we'll demonstrate it with a red sphere inside a glass sphere.</span></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544541661/myRedEye.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=522\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544541661/myRedEye.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"522\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544541678\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"myRedEye.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544541661\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5e3ed636-11ce-4bef-8cc6-2119101c7b4e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544541661/myRedEye.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1427&amp;height=582 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544541661/myRedEye.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=522 1x\"></span><p> </p><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<h3 id=\"PxrAOVLightinMaya-MayaandRIBfile\">Maya and RIB file</h3><p>Download a Maya file or inspect a RIB file for this example:</p><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/19431552/PxrAOVLight_Demo.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download</a></p>\n</div></div><h3 id=\"PxrAOVLightinMaya-LightLinkingwithPxrAOVLight\">Light Linking with PxrAOVLight</h3><p>Use light linking to include/exclude pieces of geometry in the AOV. In this example, the PxrAovLight is &quot;off&quot; globally and &quot;on&quot; for the eye in the scene.  This linking setup creates a mask of the red sphere inside the refractive glass. </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544541661/PxrAOVLight_Light_Linking.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573853&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544541661/PxrAOVLight_Light_Linking.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573853&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"383\" data-width=\"856\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544541687\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrAOVLight_Light_Linking.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544541661\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8abb84e4-b8a0-46f1-99b8-c06257c31dab\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><h3 id=\"PxrAOVLightinMaya-DefiningtheOutputAOV\">Defining the Output AOV</h3><p>Once you set an AOV Name in the PxrAOVLight attributes, use the Render Settings AOVs tab to define a new display to which PxrAovLight will write.</p><p>Make sure the names match, like so:</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"fe9350c3-dddc-45ac-84ac-9511a3f09e49\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 164.0px;\"/><col style=\"width: 106.0px;\"/></colgroup><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>PxrAOVLight</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><em>MyAOVName</em></p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>Channel Source</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><em>MyAOVName</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544541661/PxrAOVLight_Settings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544541661/PxrAOVLight_Settings.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"223\" data-width=\"452\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544541675\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrAOVLight_Settings.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544541661\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3e4ae4bb-a3a6-405b-abb4-8a0836c87257\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544541661/PxrAOVLight_AOVs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544541661/PxrAOVLight_AOVs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431573630&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"492\" data-width=\"582\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544541681\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrAOVLight_AOVs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544541661\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ca055e27-72ca-49a2-8a83-826e98659b82\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><h3 id=\"PxrAOVLightinMaya-LightFiltersandPxrAOVLight\">Light Filters and PxrAOVLight</h3><p>Because PxrAOVLight is a &quot;light&quot;, light linking and light filters can modify the output AOV. </p>"
    }
